{\f1\fs30\b\cf2 KEY RULES TO ALWAYS REMEMBER\par}
\par
\pard\li360
1.  {\b Double-check capacity and price before publishing} \emdash  these cannot be changed after going live\par
2.  {\b Link your bank account before publishing a paid (NGN) tournament} \emdash  otherwise you won\rquote t receive payments\par
3.  {\b Lock registrations before the tournament starts} \emdash  prevents last-minute sign-ups that disrupt your bracket\par
4.  {\b The platform is NOT a refund processor} \emdash  handle refunds directly with players via Paystack for one-off cases\par
5.  {\b You only need to set up your bank account once} \emdash  it stays linked for all future events\par
